content.rendered:
Serves the purpose of Table Clock. Excellent craftsmanship in both pocket watch and stand.Super Long Lighting Time, Rechargeable, Soft Bright Light & Dimmable. Built-in rechargeable 1500mAh lithium battery for around 48 hours to 10 days continuous lighting. With bright but soft light, perfect to be as a nursery night for feeding, diaper changing or sleep aid for your kids as they fall asleep.

The one-faced soft night light will not dazzle tender eyes of your babies or kids. And it is full range stepless dimmable and has last brightness memory.

excerpt.rendered: A unique table with long chain handcrafted sheesham wood stand. Simple To Set, Easy to Read, Non-Alarm & Non-Ticking. This nightlight clock is with an analog silent sweep non-alarm quartz movement, with only one button on the back, very easy to set the time.
